message: If we are facing in the right direction, all we have to do is keep on walking.
title: Thought of the day

author: Eleanor Roosevelt
message: Remember always that you not only have the right to be an individual, you have an obligation to be one.
title: Thought of the day

author: Denis Waitley
message: There are two primary choices in life: to accept conditions as they exist, or accept responsibility for changing them.
title: Thought of the day

author: Epictetus
message: If you seek truth you will not seek victory by dishonourable means, and if you find truth you will become invincible.
title: Thought of the day
